Self-proclaimed Prophet, Shepherd Bushiri, is holding a special briefing following his departure from South Africa. Editor's note: This event has ended. You may watch the recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Self-proclaimed Prophet, Shepherd Bushiri, held a special briefing following his departure from South Africa. The Bushiris have contravened their bail conditions as they are not allowed to travel outside SA. Last week, the couple was granted bail of R200,000 each. They're facing charges of theft, money laundering and fraud in connection with an alleged R100-million investment scheme.